      <title>开篇词__人人都是产品经理吗？</title>
      <link>https://politcloud.org/post/%E6%9E%81%E5%AE%A2%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4/%E8%8B%8F%E6%9D%B0%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%A7%E5%93%81%E5%88%9B%E6%96%B0%E8%AF%BE/%E5%BC%80%E7%AF%87%E8%AF%8D__%E4%BA%BA%E4%BA%BA%E9%83%BD%E6%98%AF%E4%BA%A7%E5%93%81%E7%BB%8F%E7%90%86%E5%90%97/</link>
